## Data Attribution Notice

This project references information from Amazon Seller Central public Help
pages to help sellers understand KYC requirements. The underlying policies,
documentation, and official wording belong to Amazon.com, Inc. or its
affiliates. This project is an independent tool and is NOT affiliated with,
endorsed by, or sponsored by Amazon.

Rules in `src/data/` are either:
  - Linked to public Amazon Seller Central Help pages (cited with URLs), or
  - Anonymized summaries of operational experience across multiple cases,
    with no seller-identifying information retained.

The final verification decision always rests with Amazon.
